---
import Layout from '../../layouts/Layout.astro'
---

<Layout
  titulo="Kubernetes平台 · EKS与裸金属集群"
  descripcion="EKS与裸金属环境的Kubernetes平台，集成ArgoCD GitOps、Helm和完整可观测性。首日交付生产就绪集群。"
>
  <!-- HERO -->
  <section class="relative overflow-hidden" style="background-color: #0A2540;">
    <div class="absolute inset-0 pointer-events-none opacity-40" style="background-image: radial-gradient(circle, rgba(147,184,255,0.15) 1px, transparent 1px); background-size: 28px 28px;"></div>
    <div class="relative max-w-7xl mx-auto px-6 py-20 sm:py-24">
      <div class="max-w-3xl">
        <span class="inline-flex items-center text-xs font-semibold px-4 py-2 rounded-full mb-6" style="background: rgba(30,111,255,0.15); color: #93b8ff; border: 1px solid rgba(30,111,255,0.3);">
          Kubernetes平台
        </span>
        <h1 class="text-4xl sm:text-5xl font-extrabold text-white mb-5" style="letter-spacing: -0.02em;">
          首日即可投入生产的Kubernetes集群。
        </h1>
        <p class="text-lg max-w-2xl" style="color: rgba(147,184,255,0.8);">
          从AWS EKS到裸金属集群，我们交付由ArgoCD GitOps驱动、内置Helm和完整可观测性的Kubernetes平台。
        </p>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CAPABILITIES -->
  <section class="bg-white py-16">
    <div class="max-w-5xl mx-auto px-6">
      <div class="grid sm:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-5">
        <div class="rounded-2xl p-6" style="background: #F8FAFC; border: 1px solid rgba(15,23,42,0.06);">
          <h3 class="text-base font-bold mb-2" style="color: #0A2540;">EKS集群配置</h3>
          <p class="text-sm" style="color: #64748b;">使用EKS在AWS上运行托管Kubernetes。节点组、IRSA和Cluster Autoscaler均以代码方式管理——无需控制台手动配置。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl p-6" style="background: #F8FAFC; border: 1px solid rgba(15,23,42,0.06);">
          <h3 class="text-base font-bold mb-2" style="color: #0A2540;">ArgoCD GitOps</h3>
          <p class="text-sm" style="color: #64748b;">通过ArgoCD实现持续交付，支持自动同步、剪枝和自愈。Git是集群状态的唯一事实来源。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl p-6" style="background: #F8FAFC; border: 1px solid rgba(15,23,42,0.06);">
          <h3 class="text-base font-bold mb-2" style="color: #0A2540;">Helm Chart管理</h3>
          <p class="text-sm" style="color: #64748b;">使用Helm chart和Kustomize overlay部署应用。基础配置与环境特定值之间有清晰的分离。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl p-6" style="background: #F8FAFC; border: 1px solid rgba(15,23,42,0.06);">
          <h3 class="text-base font-bold mb-2" style="color: #0A2540;">裸金属Kubernetes</h3>
          <p class="text-sm" style="color: #64748b;">使用kubeadm或k3s部署本地Kubernetes集群。生产级配置，适用于对敏感工作负载无需云依赖的场景。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl p-6" style="background: #F8FAFC; border: 1px solid rgba(15,23,42,0.06);">
          <h3 class="text-base font-bold mb-2" style="color: #0A2540;">可观测性栈</h3>
          <p class="text-sm" style="color: #64748b;">首日即集成Prometheus、Grafana和Alertmanager。涵盖集群健康状态、性能和资源使用情况的仪表盘和告警。</p>
        </div>
        <div class="rounded-2xl p-6" style="background: #F8FAFC; border: 1px solid rgba(15,23,42,0.06);">
          <h3 class="text-base font-bold mb-2" style="color: #0A2540;">网络与安全</h3>
          <p class="text-sm" style="color: #64748b;">NetworkPolicy、RBAC和Pod Security Standards均以代码方式定义。Ingress控制器配备TLS终止和限流，从一开始就已配置到位。</p>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </section>

  <!-- CTA -->
  <section style="background: #0A2540;" class="py-16">
    <div class="max-w-3xl mx-auto px-6 text-center">
      <h2 class="text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-4">准备好生产级Kubernetes平台了吗？</h2>
      <p class="text-base mb-8" style="color: rgba(147,184,255,0.8);">我们评估您当前的容器基础设施并制定具体的迁移计划。</p>
      <a href="/contact" class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 px-8 py-3.5 rounded-xl font-semibold text-white" style="background: #1E6FFF;">
        联系我们
        <svg class="w-4 h-4" fill="none" viewBox="0 0 24 24" stroke="currentColor"><path stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" stroke-width="2" d="M17 8l4 4m0 0l-4 4m4-4H3"/></svg>
      </a>
    </div>
  </section>
</Layout>
